// =============================================================================
// SUMMARY:
// This test verifies that the Iterator protocol:
// 1. Works with built-in collections (List, Array)
// 2. Works with ranges
// 3. Supports all standard iterator methods
// 4. Handles nested iteration correctly
// 5. Supports break/continue in for loops
// 6. Is resolved via protocol, not hardcoded type names
// =============================================================================
